# Dashboard design system (ArmaraOS)

- **Canonical doc:** `docs/dashboard-design-system.md` (read before styling changes).
- **Scope:** All of **`crates/openfang-api/static/`** (`css/`, `index_*.html`, **`js/**`** including **`page-load-error.js`**). **Carve-outs:** `static/vendor/**` (third-party); **`openfang-desktop/`** is native chrome, not `theme.css`.
- **Tightening:** Product UI should converge on **classes + `theme.css` tokens** (chat, settings, modals, command palette, errors, every `#hash` page). Replace inline styles / ad-hoc neutrals when editing; canvas/charts may keep programmatic colors (see doc **Exceptions**).
- **Neutrals:** Warm chromatic surfaces via `theme.css` — no scattered `#rgb` neutrals for **layout chrome**.
- **Brand:** Gold/amber (`--accent`) is for **signal**, not every border/panel.
- **Light / dark:** Warm off-white / paper light; true black + warm charcoal dark (`--surface*`).

See **Scope**, **Color palette and surfaces**, and the checklist in `docs/dashboard-design-system.md`.
